---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="HomeKeep — Support">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">HomeKeep Support</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">We're here to help.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 mb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">How do I restore my Pro purchase on a new device?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Go to Settings → Restore Purchases. Make sure you're signed in with the same Apple ID you used to purchase.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 mb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">How do I sync my tasks between devices?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">HomeKeep syncs automatically through iCloud. Make sure iCloud is enabled in your iPhone Settings → [Your Name] → iCloud.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 mb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">I'm not getting reminders</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Check that notifications are enabled: Settings → Notifications → HomeKeep → Allow Notifications. Also make sure Do Not Disturb isn't blocking them.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 mb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Can I add my own custom tasks?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Yes! Tap the + button on the main screen to create a custom task with your own name, frequency, category, and notes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 mb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">What's the difference between Free and Pro?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Free gives you up to 8 maintenance tasks. Pro ($4.99, one-time) unlocks unlimited tasks, home screen widgets, and complete history tracking. No subscription — buy once, yours forever.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Still Need Help?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">I respond to every email within 24 hours.</p>
    <a href="mailto:justinbundrick@gmail.com" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">Email Support</a>

    <p class="mt-12 text-gray-500 text-sm">© 2026 Justin Bundrick</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
